{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-awesome-readme-js","path":"/seancoyne/awesome-coldfusion/readme/","result":{"data":{"site":{"siteMetadata":{"title":"Track Awesome List"}},"markdownRemark":{"id":"af976252-b738-58a8-a1e9-2171f22a6762","html":"<h1 id=\"awesome-coldfusion-awesome\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#awesome-coldfusion-awesome\" aria-label=\"awesome coldfusion awesome permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Awesome ColdFusion <a href=\"https://github.com/sindresorhus/awesome\"><img src=\"https://cdn.rawgit.com/sindresorhus/awesome/d7305f38d29fed78fa85652e3a63e154dd8e8829/media/badge.svg\" alt=\"Awesome\"></a></h1>\n<p>A curated list of awesome ColdFusion frameworks, libraries and software. Inspired by <a href=\"https://github.com/sorrycc/awesome-javascript\">awesome-javascript</a><a data-role=\"trackawesomelist-badge\" href=\"https://github.com/sorrycc/awesome-javascript\" style=\"text-decoration:none;top: -2px;position: relative;margin-left:4px;margin-right:4px;font-weight:400;\"><span style=\"color: #fff;font-size: 11px;font-family: Verdana, Geneva, DejaVu Sans,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"padding:4px 4px 4px 6px;background: #555;border-top-left-radius: 4px;border-bottom-left-radius: 4px;\">stars</span><span style=\"padding: 4px 6px 4px 4px;background: #007ec6;border-top-right-radius: 4px;border-bottom-right-radius: 4px;\">24k</span></span></a>.</p>\n<p>Pull requests very welcome.</p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/seancoyne/awesome-coldfusion\">Awesome ColdFusion</a><a data-role=\"trackawesomelist-badge\" href=\"https://github.com/seancoyne/awesome-coldfusion\" style=\"text-decoration:none;top: -2px;position: relative;margin-left:4px;margin-right:4px;font-weight:400;\"><span style=\"color: #fff;font-size: 11px;font-family: Verdana, Geneva, DejaVu Sans,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"padding:4px 4px 4px 6px;background: #555;border-top-left-radius: 4px;border-bottom-left-radius: 4px;\">stars</span><span style=\"padding: 4px 6px 4px 4px;background: #007ec6;border-top-right-radius: 4px;border-bottom-right-radius: 4px;\">81</span></span></a>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"#engines\">Engines</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#application-frameworks\">Application Frameworks</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#testing\">Testing</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#dependency-injection\">Dependency Injection</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#cms\">Content Management Systems</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#nosql\">NoSQL</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#rest\">REST</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#other-libraries\">Other Libraries</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#editors\">Editors</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#tools\">Tools</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#references\">References</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#resources\">Resources</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#documentation\">Documentation</a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<hr>\n<h2 id=\"engines\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#engines\" aria-label=\"engines permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Engines</h2>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"http://www.adobe.com/products/coldfusion-family.html\">Adobe ColdFusion</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"http://lucee.org/\">Lucee</a> - Free, Open Source CFML Engine, Fork of <a href=\"http://www.getrailo.org/\">Railo</a></li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"application-frameworks\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#application-frameworks\" aria-label=\"application frameworks permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Application Frameworks</h2>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://cfwheels.org\">CFWheels</a> - An open source CFML framework inspired by Ruby on Rails.</li>\n<li><a href=\"http://www.coldbox.org\">ColdBox</a> - The Enterprise ColdFusion MVC Development Platform</li>\n<li><a href=\"http://www.farcrycore.org\">FarCry</a> - FarCry Core is a web application framework that helps CFML developers build tailor-made content solutions, fast.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/framework-one/fw1\">FW/1 - Framework One</a><a data-role=\"trackawesomelist-badge\" href=\"https://github.com/framework-one/fw1\" style=\"text-decoration:none;top: -2px;position: relative;margin-left:4px;margin-right:4px;font-weight:400;\"><span style=\"color: #fff;font-size: 11px;font-family: Verdana, Geneva, DejaVu Sans,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"padding:4px 4px 4px 6px;background: #555;border-top-left-radius: 4px;border-bottom-left-radius: 4px;\">stars</span><span style=\"padding: 4px 6px 4px 4px;background: #007ec6;border-top-right-radius: 4px;border-bottom-right-radius: 4px;\">371</span></span></a> - a lightweight, convention over configuration, MVC application framework</li>\n<li><a href=\"http://model-glue.com\">ModelGlue</a> - a CFML based, full stack, front controller based on MVC. Features include Scaffolding, ORM integration, and many others</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"testing\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#testing\" aria-label=\"testing permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Testing</h2>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/teamcfadvance/CFSelenium\">CFSelenium</a><a data-role=\"trackawesomelist-badge\" href=\"https://github.com/teamcfadvance/CFSelenium\" style=\"text-decoration:none;top: -2px;position: relative;margin-left:4px;margin-right:4px;font-weight:400;\"><span style=\"color: #fff;font-size: 11px;font-family: Verdana, Geneva, DejaVu Sans,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"padding:4px 4px 4px 6px;background: #555;border-top-left-radius: 4px;border-bottom-left-radius: 4px;\">stars</span><span style=\"padding: 4px 6px 4px 4px;background: #007ec6;border-top-right-radius: 4px;border-bottom-right-radius: 4px;\">78</span></span></a> - A native Selenium RC binding for ColdFusion</li>\n<li><a href=\"http://wiki.coldbox.org/wiki/MockBox.cfm\">MockBox</a> - The ColdFusion Mocking/Stubbing Framework</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/mxunit/mxunit\">MXUnit</a><a data-role=\"trackawesomelist-badge\" href=\"https://github.com/mxunit/mxunit\" style=\"text-decoration:none;top: -2px;position: relative;margin-left:4px;margin-right:4px;font-weight:400;\"><span style=\"color: #fff;font-size: 11px;font-family: Verdana, Geneva, DejaVu Sans,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"padding:4px 4px 4px 6px;background: #555;border-top-left-radius: 4px;border-bottom-left-radius: 4px;\">stars</span><span style=\"padding: 4px 6px 4px 4px;background: #007ec6;border-top-right-radius: 4px;border-bottom-right-radius: 4px;\">88</span></span></a> - xUnit style unit testing framework</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/atuttle/mxunit-watch\">mxunit-watch</a><a data-role=\"trackawesomelist-badge\" href=\"https://github.com/atuttle/mxunit-watch\" style=\"text-decoration:none;top: -2px;position: relative;margin-left:4px;margin-right:4px;font-weight:400;\"><span style=\"color: #fff;font-size: 11px;font-family: Verdana, Geneva, DejaVu Sans,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"padding:4px 4px 4px 6px;background: #555;border-top-left-radius: 4px;border-bottom-left-radius: 4px;\">stars</span><span style=\"padding: 4px 6px 4px 4px;background: #007ec6;border-top-right-radius: 4px;border-bottom-right-radius: 4px;\">14</span></span></a> - watch a directory for file changes (.cfc, .cfm, .xml) to trigger mxunit test suite full run, displaying results in the console</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/Ortus-Solutions/TestBox\">TestBox</a><a data-role=\"trackawesomelist-badge\" href=\"https://github.com/Ortus-Solutions/TestBox\" style=\"text-decoration:none;top: -2px;position: relative;margin-left:4px;margin-right:4px;font-weight:400;\"><span style=\"color: #fff;font-size: 11px;font-family: Verdana, Geneva, DejaVu Sans,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"padding:4px 4px 4px 6px;background: #555;border-top-left-radius: 4px;border-bottom-left-radius: 4px;\">stars</span><span style=\"padding: 4px 6px 4px 4px;background: #007ec6;border-top-right-radius: 4px;border-bottom-right-radius: 4px;\">45</span></span></a> - BDD style unit testing framework</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"dependency-injection\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#dependency-injection\" aria-label=\"dependency injection permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" heigh